Term-BashTab
=========================

A simple wrapper of Term::ReadLine, offerring bash-like <TAB> feature.

It is useful when you need an interactive session asking a valid path
from term-user.

It makes use of the completion stub offerred by Term::ReadLine
(actually Term::ReadLine::*).

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Term::ReadLine

